title: HAKODATE UNIT CARNIVAL
description: Saint Snow Presents Love Live! Sunshine!! HAKODATE UNIT CARNIVAL is a live concert that took place at Hakodate Arena on April 27 & 28, 2018. It featured the subunits CYaRon!, AZALEA, Guilty Kiss and Saint Snow. Balloting tickets for the concert were included with each copy of Awaken the power.
